Package: flixpatrol
Type: Package
Title: R Client for the 'FlixPatrol' Streaming Rankings API
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Alejandro", "Hagan",
      email = "alejandro.hagan@outlook.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides a programmatic interface to the 'FlixPatrol' API (V2) for
    accessing streaming platform rankings, viewing hours, official charts,
    torrent data, and social media fan metrics. Includes lookup helpers for
    countries, platforms, franchises, and titles.
